{"tid":968852,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[建立品牌2] 呢對迷人既眼，請你殺死我啦~","createTime":"2019-01-04T14:51:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-27T22:51:40.000Z","uid":229185,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a72d6688ab03054094a9dd0af820ecda03dbb4d7","tid":968852,"uid":229185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T14:51:31.000Z","msg":"舊POST~<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/963679/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/963679/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n琴日去左運動場做下運動，咁做完當然去沖涼啦，唔係臭臭豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁可能我沖涼果陣啲涷水激發左我腦海裡面啲創意力，當我沖完既時候換衫。<br />\n我見到呢個&quot;小心保管你的財物&quot; 呢個貼紙<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UyrktMZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUyrktMZ.jpg&h=646a47ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我深信好多巴打絲打一定見過呢雙迷人既眼睛係更衣室度，呢對外國人既雙眼真係靚到殺死人，令到啲想偷嘢既人想停一停，諗三諗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n加上呢張貼紙好似爛哂， 作為有愛心有公德心既香港人，姐係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗住幫幫香港政府設計重新既貼紙 ，有本土味，真。香港風，令人感覺有威嚴同怕既感覺<br />\n免收設計費<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n首先諗諗個設計所用既眼睛，巴打絲打要諗下，有本土味同真。香港風，姐係必係香港人啦!!!<br />\n唔通搵個洋腸咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第二， 我想問下係香港有邊個令人感覺有威嚴同怕怕既感覺， 我相信大家都同意係我都公正嚴明既律政司司長<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NoM1djw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNoM1djw.jpg&h=06e30cb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我用左好耐時間，設計左令香港盜竊率大幅下降既設計~<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PTJV2dy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPTJV2dy.jpg&h=2f4f6242&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n等我貼返張新既貼紙先~~~<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DtVYfzk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDtVYfzk.jpg&h=93a647fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LF1TOVK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLF1TOVK.jpg&h=7e7ff2d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇到呢對迷人既眼， 你都唔敢偷香港人野啦。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n本人建議將貼紙貼去房署，用鄭若驊司長既威嚴去感化房署等候既人士<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2236596/%E6%B8%AF%E7%94%B7%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E5%85%AC%E5%B1%8B%E8%A6%8B%E8%81%9E%E9%8C%84%E3%80%80%E8%A2%AB%E6%99%AE%E9%80%9A%E8%A9%B1%E4%BA%BA%E5%8C%85%E5%9C%8D%E7%88%AD%E8%B3%87%E6%BA%90\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2236596%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%2594%25B7%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25AB%258B%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25B1%258B%25E8%25A6%258B%25E8%2581%259E%25E9%258C%2584%25E3%2580%2580%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%2599%25AE%25E9%2580%259A%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%258C%2585%25E5%259C%258D%25E7%2588%25AD%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%25BA%2590&d=VDOKtd8IA5ycP%2BmwAMRj6zQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=015dd625\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2236596/%E6%B8%AF%E7%94%B7%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E5%85%AC%E5%B1%8B%E8%A6%8B%E8%81%9E%E9%8C%84%E3%80%80%E8%A2%AB%E6%99%AE%E9%80%9A%E8%A9%B1%E4%BA%BA%E5%8C%85%E5%9C%8D%E7%88%AD%E8%B3%87%E6%BA%90</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n作為連登首個偽時裝牌子，點都整件衫出嚟，扮下野先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hx01XRo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHx01XRo.jpg&h=c5c84d75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為呢個設計真係免費比住香港政府去整，作為香港人你地點都支持下我掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/sleazy.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fsleazy.hk%2F&d=VDOKtd8IA5ycP%2BmwAMRj6zQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=aaabe7da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/sleazy.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\nTG: <a href=\"https://telegram.me/sleazy_hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftelegram.me%2Fsleazy_hk&d=VDOKtd8IA5ycP%2BmwAMRj6zQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=14ba5b79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://telegram.me/sleazy_hk</a><br />\n(希望大家比意見可以將呢張貼紙貼去邊呢)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多謝你地浪費左一分鐘既人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/battle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84b340e8d253d24326cce11c6f5a47bf0dd9b359","tid":968852,"uid":147916,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T04:10:24.000Z","msg":"又幾正喎，想問喺邊度有呢啲貼紙？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60e4e7f61bde412e17971ad4867ce6e66a8709a1","tid":968852,"uid":229185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84b340e8d253d24326cce11c6f5a47bf0dd9b359","tid":968852,"uid":147916,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T04:10:24.000Z","msg":"又幾正喎，想問喺邊度有呢啲貼紙？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T22:51:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n未整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}